Package org.dspace.sword2

Class WorkflowManagerUnrestricted

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.sword2.WorkflowManagerUnrestricted
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WorkflowManager
    public class WorkflowManagerUnrestricted
extends Object
implements WorkflowManager
    This implementation of WorkflowManager is unrestricted and allows UPDATE and DELETE operations on items in any state (in workflow, in archive, or withdrawn).
